## How to run a review

1. Make your changes and commit them.
2. Run `contextur review --base {{base_branch}}` to generate a structured review request.
3. Feed the output to your AI IDE (Claude Code, Cursor, Codex, or any AI assistant).
4. The AI follows the 3-stage pipeline: specialist reviewers → challenger → synthesizer.

Reviewer prompts live in `.contextur/reviewers/`. They are plain Markdown — edit them, commit them, treat them like code.

